            . I am the son of John Ironside, a <rs id="t18280911-351-viclabel1808" type="occupation">carpenter</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280911-351-victim1903 t18280911-351-viclabel1808"></join>, who lives on Saffron-hill. I went into the back room on the 8th of August; I heard a footstep in the front parlour - I came out and saw the prisoner going out; I followed and overtook her just outside the door - she threw this caddy from her apron; a person picked it up, and gave it to me - the officer took her.</p>
