            . I am an officer and took the prisoner.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I went in for one penny worth of milk; I stood by the door, and while I was waiting, one of the cows turned round with great fury - I ran back with fright, and knocked this down against the door; I never had it in my apron nor near it - had I thrown it down, it would have broken.</p>
